window.bookSummaryJSON = "When last seen, Jack and Stephen had been shipwrecked on a desert island in the glittering South China Sea. <i>The Nutmeg of Consolation</i> opens as the castaways fashion a makeshift vessel from the wreckage, only to have it destroyed in a fiery attack by Malay pirates. Only the wondrous ingenuity of Stephen, along with the unexpected appearance of one of Jack's oldest allies, leads them to escape, and to dubious safety in a penal colony at New South Wales.The fourteenth installment of Patrick O'Brian's hugely successful Aubrey/Maturin series."; 
